		<td><b>Re: <span class="posthilit">SNES</span> vs Genesis</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There is no software rendering involved, only per frame <span class="posthilit">vertical</span> scroll changes for the stretching. Horizontal scrolls are most probably handled by the <span class="posthilit">line</span> scroll table, it makes little sense to handle these realtime.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


